<h2>Logical properties</h2>
<p>When working with rtl layouts, prefer logical properties to their
  physical counterparts. For example, use <code>margin-inline-start</code>
  instead of <code>margin-left</code>. This will ensure that your
  styles are applied correctly regardless of the text direction.</p>
</p>

